name: Quadravest Preferred Split Share ETF
longDescription: The investment objectives of the Quadravest Preferred Split Share ETF are to provide Unitholders of the ETF with: (a) monthly distributions and (b) the opportunity for capital preservation primarily through investment in a portfolio of preferred shares of split share corporations.
fulldescription: The investment objectives of the Quadravest Preferred Split Share ETF are to provide Unitholders of the ETF with: (a) monthly distributions and (b) the opportunity for capital preservation primarily through investment in a portfolio of preferred shares of split share corporations. The ETF may also invest in preferred shares of other issuers, exchange-traded funds, other investment funds, equities or income-generating securities, The investment objectives of the Quadravest Preferred Split Share ETF are to provide Unitholders of the ETF
